"Controls :\n"
" Keyboard :\n"
"  `    -> show/hide console\n"
"  ~    -> state snapshot\n"
"  +, - -> change LOD\n"
"  Esc  -> exit\n"
" Mouse :\n"
"  left button  -> horizontal move\n"
"  right button -> rotation\n"
"  both         -> vertical move\n"
" Console :\n"
"  help                     -> show this help message\n"
"  blending / alphatesting  -> change Blending/Alpha testing"
